\n<li><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Aerys I's</a> (~210-?)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Kaeth\" title=\"Kaeth\">Kaeth</a> (257-258)<sup>2</sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Ellendor\" title=\"Ellendor\">Ellendor</a> (258-259)<sup>2</sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Merion\" title=\"Merion\">Merion</a> (259)<sup>7</sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Pycelle\" title=\"Pycelle\">Pycelle</a> (259-300)</li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr style=\"height:2px\"><td></td></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\";;\">Grand Maesters<br />of unknown terms</td><td style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-even\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Aethelmure\" title=\"Aethelmure\">Aethelmure</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Clegg\" title=\"Clegg\">Clegg</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Greydon\" title=\"Greydon\">Greydon</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Hareth_(Grand_Maester)\" title=\"Hareth (Grand Maester)\">Hareth</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Lucan_(Grand_Maester)\" title=\"Lucan (Grand Maester)\">Lucan</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Malleon\" title=\"Malleon\">Malleon</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr style=\"height:2px\"><td></td></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\";;\">Grand Maesters<br />to claimants and usurpers</td><td style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Gerardys\" title=\"Gerardys\">Gerardys</a> (129-130)<sup>8</sup></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr style=\"height:2px;\"><td></td></tr><tr><td class=\"navbox-abovebelow\" style=\";\" colspan=\"2\"><div>\n<ul><li><sup>1</sup> Position created</li>\n<li><sup>2</sup> Died within a year of being named</li>\n<li><sup>3</sup> Executed by King <a href=\"/index.php/Maegor_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Maegor I Targaryen\">Maegor I Targaryen</a></li>\n<li><sup>4</sup> Munkun is known to have been the Grand Maester before and after Alford</li>\n<li><sup>5</sup> Also served as <a href=\"/index.php/Hand_of_the_King\" title=\"Hand of the King\">Hand of the King</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Regent\" title=\"Regent\">Regent</a></li>\n<li><sup>6</sup> Known to have been the Grand Maester in <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_153_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">153&#160;AC</a></li>\n<li><sup>7</sup> Died en route to King's Landing</li>\n<li><sup>8</sup> Previously served as Maester at Dragonstone</li></ul>\n</div></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\"border-spacing:0;;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:2px;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks hlist mw-collapsible mw-collapsed collapsible autocollapse navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;width:100%;color:inherit;;;\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" style=\";\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2\"><div class=\"plainlinks hlist\" style=\"display:block;float:left;font-weight:normal;font-size:88%;padding-top:3px;text-align:left;width:6.8em;\"><ul><li class=\"nv-view\"><a href=\"/index.php/Template:Aerys_I_small_council\" title=\"Template:Aerys I small council\"><span title=\"View this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">v</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-talk\"><a href=\"/index.php?title=Template_talk:Aerys_I_small_council&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Template talk:Aerys I small council (page does not exist)\"><span title=\"Discuss this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">d</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-edit\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://awoiaf.westeros.org/index.php?title=Template:Aerys_I_small_council&amp;action=edit\"><span title=\"Edit this template\" style=\";;background:n